Comment: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:12.08,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.64,0:00:30.85,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}suujuuoku mono kodou no kazu sae
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.64,0:00:30.85,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Even the world's billions of heartbeats
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.85,0:00:37.78,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}anata ni wa matataki teido no saji na toukyuu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.85,0:00:37.78,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Are nothing to you but a fleeting and insignificant question
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.78,0:00:42.82,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}kako ni torawarete mirai wo nageku mo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.78,0:00:42.82,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}We may be trapped in the past or lament the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.82,0:00:48.75,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}chiri hitotsu gosan wo yurusanu hitsuzen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.82,0:00:48.75,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}But predetermination does not allow the slightest mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:55.00,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}mugen ni hirogaru yume mo egaku mirai mo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:55.00,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}The infinite dreams and imagined futures before us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:01:00.80,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}bokutachi ni yurusareta kyoei no genri
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:01:00.80,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Are naught but vain theories we may hold
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.80,0:01:06.85,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,250)}yuugen sore wa futatsu no hari ga shimesu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.80,0:01:06.85,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,250)}Finitude is what the two clock hands show
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.85,0:01:11.60,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(250,0)}zankoku na yakujou to sentaku e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.85,0:01:11.60,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(250,0)}As they point toward a cruel destiny and choice
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:13.52,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Hacking to the Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.52,0:01:20.74,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(1000,0}dakara ima ichibyou goto ni sekaisen wo koete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.52,0:01:20.74,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(1000,0}And now I cross the boundary between worlds each second
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:25.78,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}kimi no sono egao mamoritai no sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:25.78,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Because I want to protect that smile of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.78,0:01:32.71,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}soshite mata kanashimi no nai jikan no ruupu e to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.78,0:01:32.71,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}And a loop in time without sadness will once again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:38.96,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}nomikomarete yuku kodoku no kansokusha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:38.96,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Engulf me, a lonely observer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.47,0:01:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.01,0:01:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep lying there, you'll get heatstroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sleep on the roof of the lab all the time, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:01:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's cloudy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.19,0:02:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashida said he couldn't find her at Comima...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.11,0:02:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met up with her after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Okabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.58,0:02:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.27,0:02:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! {This line was originally "WTF?!" but no. Just no.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you warn me earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm soaked, down to my underwear...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault, Christina, for not listen{\fscx80}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't trying to look...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's your fault for wearing such thin clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd forgotten you were such a pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd want to see your stick figure in the nude{\fscx80}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more word, and I turn your neocortex into a flower pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of threat is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got scratched somewhere, when I was looking for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Klutz!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm classified as a "mad scientist"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so much trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand that over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a sewing kit on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fix it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sewing kit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I consider myself more family-oriented
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,than most people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:49.59,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Just to be clear,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:52.72,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,it's dark, so don't expect too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:56.52,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx74}And you can look forward to finding out what color thread I used after we leave. {Thinking this might be too much of a squeeze}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:58.98,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Black, red, pink...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:00.65,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a 33% chance of each one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:03.32,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just pray it isn't pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:05.53,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in that stick figure of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you... A flower pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you have to go, to rip your clothes like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I went to the lab,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the laundry,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then to your hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hotel? You stopped by?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't answer my messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't picking up your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.14,0:04:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you worried about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As head of the lab, it's my job to keep track of my assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cold. Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just put it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in the stick figure of a nude mad scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably around here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place I was stabbed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.77,0:05:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain and despair were too real for a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurisu. You can't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have hazy memories inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weak, almost nonexistent memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just of being stabbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember you, too... hazily...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How desperate you were to save Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How you kept pressing forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:05:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even hurt and all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't made it back to your original world,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you've kept going,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,kept calling her name,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,kept crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kept trying to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I see that face,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think about how important she is to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And about whether it's possible for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to truly care for another person that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I wanted to work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I wanted to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe, save Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:07:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go to the beta world line, you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the only way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that better than anyone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one option.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me to abandon you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there another way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about the following since yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.93,0:07:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Isn't there some other way?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Isn't there something else we can do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this time, I can't come up with anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Except going to the beta world line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to accept this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't abandon Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't let her die and then keep living.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What would the point of that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can run away, but that'll just make it worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times you time leap,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can't get past the 1% barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know until we try!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll just see Mayuri die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll destroy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do you think I've watched her die?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:09:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And again and again and again
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and again and again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't destroy me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The number of times I see it doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hear what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri's going to suffer and die...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say it doesn't matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that doesn't affect you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then your heart's already broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or it really will break you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.48,0:09:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I noticed it long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.57,0:09:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times Mayuri died, \NI stopped being surprised. {This line doesn't really make sense but I have no idea what it's supposed to be}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd gone numb without even knowing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, I even waited before time leaping, \Njust to see when she'd die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At some point,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it just stopped affecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere inside, I was calmly telling myself that I could do it over...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, it will destroy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you let her die, you'll regret it... I'm certain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I have come this far, from the single wish to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we stop, we'll always regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we save her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the first world line, before the D-mail was sent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's best for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's what's best for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How many times have we fought, \Nover these past twenty days?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've made fun of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've talked about our problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When my back was against the wall, I turned to Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.53,0:11:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kurisu was the one who listened to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.82,0:11:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who believed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At eighteen, a genius with a published academic paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always calm, always strong-willed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always so proud and nosy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But always so kind and honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.13,0:11:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her theories continually amazed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I remembered everything she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Watched everything she did...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She wasn't just another lab member.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To me, Makise Kurisu was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't save you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,0:11:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For suffering so much for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what does it mean to change world lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the second you go to the beta world line,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll just disappear from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe you trade places with another Okabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm dead in the beta world line,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no guarantee that I'm going to die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There could be another me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,amidst all the other, infinite world lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And our minds are connected and comprise "me."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.43,0:13:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that'd be wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be everywhere, in every time, at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A great love for someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.07,0:13:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a great belief in something,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a great desire to pass on something...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If all those things surpass time itself and create "you,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't that be wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't think of it as abandoning me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the world line changes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.22,0:13:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as you don't forget me, I'm there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.05,0:13:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget the person I care for most.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How... It's so sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:13:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear your response.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face... Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I didn't want to do that, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But experiences, such as your first kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:15:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that are stored in the hippocampus with your strong memories are harder to forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.26,0:15:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't my first kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bratty virgin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, virgin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My first kiss wasn't at all romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That last one only left a weak impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.91,0:15:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to forget, not ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll take extra care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a kiss, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Time is passing so quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, I feel like complaining to Einstein.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know, Okabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether time is slow or fast
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}depends on perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Relativity theory is so romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure about not saying it to Mayuri and Daru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone seeing me off would just make it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.38,0:16:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's only you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.17,0:16:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can leave Japan without any hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:25.72,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:26.77,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:29.73,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:32.94,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,I upgraded it to version 2.67.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:34.94,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.94,0:16:36.86,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll take it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.59,0:17:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you throwing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye. {She mouths "Sayounara". Is "Goodbye" final enough? Should I even sub this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure, whatever happens, you're going to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only you will remember me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in a world where no one else does.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}More than anyone else, you care for your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so that'll be painful for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.19,0:17:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But somehow, I'm glad you'll have that pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:58.32,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those times when you're sitting around the lab...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:00.49,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you drink a can of juice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.90,0:18:02.53,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you walk around town...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:06.62,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And someday, when you kiss someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.74,0:18:10.50,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't have to be every time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:12.54,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It can be one time out of a hundred...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.54,0:18:14.37,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'd like you to remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because I'll be there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be there, beyond the 1% barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.88,0:18:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin, I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is totally it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we delete this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:19:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We now begin the final phase of Operation Verdandi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our victory is nigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.92,0:19:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have overcome all conspiracies...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upholding our ideals to the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, we have fought through the battle of Ragnarok!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thank those who have worked so hard for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to ensure this victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am grateful to all those I have had to sacrifice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What comes now is the world I wished for!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all the choice of Steins Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be rebuilt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kurisu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:19:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:19:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.02,0:20:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also in...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is Lab Member 004?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.75,0:20:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,004?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.17,0:20:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't an 004.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the battle of Ragnarok has ended!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, the mad scientist, Hououin Kyouma, \Nhave controlled time itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.32,0:20:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,foiling the Organization and SERN's schemes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and bringing about complete victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's ruling structure has been reset!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a future of chaos awaits!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:21:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the choice of Steins Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.30,0:21:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just issued a declaration of victory...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to talk like that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii is okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.51,0:21:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you can cry for yourself, Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We no longer need the Phone Microwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because of it, I met Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But because of it, so many were hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as Hououin Kyouma has died,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.08,0:21:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Phone Microwave should die, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Living should mean no do-overs...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.59,0:21:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(0,1600)}This is for the best. Right, Kurisu?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.58,0:23:02.45,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.04,0:23:05.21,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wh-Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.04,0:23:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.46,0:23:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.50,0:23:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.96,0:23:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin, there's a mysterious girl who wants to talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.67,0:23:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.42,0:23:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come to the Radio Building's roof immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.05,0:23:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.14,0:23:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come from the year 2036.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.02,0:23:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hashida Itaru's daughter, Amane Suzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.64,0:23:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.60,0:23:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.86,0:23:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please believe what I'm about to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.40,0:23:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must stop World War III. {OHHHHHHHHHHHH SNAP}
